      <title>里夫斯称预算将增税 400 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/reeves-says-budget-raises-taxes-by-40-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯在伦敦下议院向议员发表讲话时表示，她的预算将使税收增加 400 亿英镑（518 亿美元）。“今天站在这里的任何财政大臣都必须面对这一现实，任何负责任的财政大臣都会采取行动，”里夫斯说。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/reeves-says-budget-raises-taxes-by-40-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:21:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家克劳迪娅·萨姆：GDP 报告“没什么可怕的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/gdp-report-not-one-to-be-afraid-of-economist-claudia-sahm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新世纪顾问公司首席经济学家 Claudia Sahm 表示，对美国经济来说，“好消息就是好消息”，她认为“目前的趋势比疫情爆发时要好得多”。她加入了“彭博监测”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/gdp-report-not-one-to-be-afraid-of-economist-claudia-sahm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国通胀大幅上升，凸显欧洲央行面临的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/german-inflation-ticks-up-sharply-highlighting-ecb-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国通胀率加速上涨，超出预期，并超过了欧洲央行2%的目标——这给政策制定者在决定进一步放松货币政策的速度和程度时带来了挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/german-inflation-ticks-up-sharply-highlighting-ecb-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 利润反弹，零售需求成为症结所在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/coinbase-retail-demand-becomes-a-sticking-point-while-profit-rebounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于许多散户交易者似乎仍然对动荡的加密货币世界保持警惕，第三季度收入的激增可能不足以消除围绕 Coinbase Global Inc. 的投资者的犹豫情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/coinbase-retail-demand-becomes-a-sticking-point-while-profit-rebounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:04:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
